textBox.richText: Xmas break day #1 had 8” of snow on the ground...another S7 day! Alli brought out the bandits, and we did a bunch of runs together...starting with the warm-up run down outhouse. Note: still sketchy. Hi-Lo trees and Pioneer were where the best snow was...they also opened up the north side of the bowl, which meant you could do the upper switchyard trees.
